     "Board" means the F i e Brigade Board established under the Act;
     "Brigade" means the Jamaica Fire Brigade;
     "Chairman" means the Chairman of the Board;
     "Commissioner" means the Commissioner of the Jamaica Fite
         Brigade;
     "fire service" means service in the Brigade;
